#  Finwise - Personal Finance Tracker

![GitHub repo size](https://img.shields.io/github/repo-size/your-username/finwise)
![GitHub stars](https://img.shields.io/github/stars/your-username/finwise?style=social)
![GitHub forks](https://img.shields.io/github/forks/your-username/finwise?style=social)
![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-green)

A lightweight and user-friendly **personal finance tracker** built using **Vanilla JavaScript**.
Track your income, expenses, and financial trends — directly in your browser with no backend required.

---

## ✨ Demo

👉 *Add your live demo link here (GitHub Pages / Netlify)*

---

## 🚀 Features

* 📊 **Real-time Dashboard**

  * Balance, Income, Expense overview

* 📈 **Visual Analytics**

  * Line chart for balance trends
  * Pie chart for expense distribution

* 🧾 **Transaction Management**

  * Add / Edit / Delete transactions
  * Filter by type & category
  * Search and sort functionality

* 🌙 **Dark Mode Support**

  * Persistent theme using localStorage

* 🔐 **Role-Based Access**

  * Admin → full control
  * Viewer → read-only

* 💾 **Local Storage Persistence**

  * No database required

* 📤 **Export to CSV**

  * Download all transactions easily

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

* **HTML5**
* **CSS3**
* **JavaScript (ES6)**
* **Chart.js**
* **Font Awesome**

